# ============================================================================
# Export Options Explanation:
# ============================================================================
# rw                 : Read-write access
# sync               : Commit writes before replying to clients
# no_subtree_check  : Disable security checks for performance (acceptable for lab)
# no_root_squash    : Allow Admin pod root to provision home directories
# insecure           : Permit containerized clients using high source ports
#
# WARNING: These are lab settings. A stricter production export should use:
#   - root_squash with a controlled provisioning path
#   - secure ports if clients can use privileged source ports
#   - tighter client IP ranges
# ============================================================================
